msgid ""
"Before being inserted into the floccualtor channel, the baffle module is "
"constructed as a unit as shown here."
msgstr ""

#: ../../Flocculation/Floc_Design.rst:140
msgid ""
"AguaClara flocculators, like the one pictured above, are called "
"**vertical hydraulic flocculators** because the baffles force the flow "
"vertically up and down. If the baffles were instead arranged to force the"
" flow side-to-side, the flocculator would be called a **horizontal "
